# 2025-11-28 21:29:58.188976
+The ballon must randomly have different color. White, yellow, orange, green, blue, red, and black. Two white make a yellow, two yellow make an orange, two green make a blue, two blue make red, and two red make a black, and two balck make the balloon disappear. the level is completed when there is no more ballon. 10 points for white merge, 20 for yellow, 30 for orange, 40 for green, 50 for blue, 60 for red and 100 for black

